<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I'm curious on others' thoughts about Kenny. Is George potentially falling in love with Kenny, or is Kenny simply a reminder to him of what it's like to appreciate life? That is, right before the end of the book, when George becomes determined to embrace his life anew, is it because he has found Kenny or because Kenny has changed his perspective? Or both? I'd love to hear what others think about this. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
